103
00:11:24,412 --> 00:11:27,760
PROŠLA NOÆ JE BILA GREŠKA.

104
00:11:27,795 --> 00:11:31,405
...I NOÆ PRIJE...

105
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:35,440
SIGURNO SAM PUNO GRIJEŠILA
OVAJ TJEDAN.

106
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:50,800
ŽELIŠ LI DA ODEM?

107
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:34,960
MALI POKLON...

108
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:44,365
PREDIVNA JE.

109
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:47,840
ALI JE NE MOGU NOSITI.

110
00:12:47,875 --> 00:12:51,280
MENELAJ BI NAS UBIO OBOJE.

111
00:12:51,315 --> 00:12:54,657
NE BOJ SE NJEGA.

112
00:12:54,692 --> 00:12:58,000
NE BOJIM SE UMIRANJA

113
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:02,800
BOJIM SE ZA SUTRA...

114
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:08,560
BOJIM SE DA ÆEŠ OTIÆI I NIKAD SE
NE VRATITI.

115
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:15,200
PRIJE NEGO SI DOŠAO U SPARTU...

116
00:13:15,235 --> 00:13:17,965
.. BILA SAM KAO DUH.

117
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:22,000
MISLILA SAM DA NEMA NADE.

118
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:24,685
...KAO DUH.

119
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:28,720
NE MORAŠ BRINUTI ZA SUTRA.

120
00:13:28,755 --> 00:13:32,560
POÐI SA MNOM.

121
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,320
NE POIGRAVAJ SE MNOME.

122
00:13:35,355 --> 00:13:37,277
...NE IGRAJ SE.

123
00:13:37,312 --> 00:13:39,085
AKO POÐEŠ...

124
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:41,120
...NEÆEMO PRONAÆI SIGURNOST.

125
00:13:41,155 --> 00:13:42,925
PROGONIT ÆE NAS...

126
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,960
PROKLET ÆE NAS BOGOVI...

127
00:13:44,995 --> 00:13:47,725
ALI JA TE VOLIM.

128
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:51,760
DO DANA KAD MI TIJELO SPALE...

129
00:13:51,795 --> 00:13:55,600
...JA ÆU TE VOLJETI.

130
00:14:13,680 --> 00:14:15,565
PREKRASNO JUTRO.

131
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:19,405
SUNCE JE BLAGOSLOVILO NAS PUT.

132
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:23,440
PONEKAD TE BOGOVI BLAGOSLOVE UJUTRO
A NAVEÈE BACE PROKLETSTVO.

133
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:29,965
VOLIŠ LI ME BRATE?

134
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:34,000
BRANIT ÆEŠ ME OD NEPRIJATELJA?

135
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:37,760
ZADNJI PUT SI OVAKO PRIÈAO
KAD SI IMAO 10 GODINA...

136
00:14:37,795 --> 00:14:41,680
.. I UPRAVO SI UKRAO OÈEVOG KONJA.

137
00:14:41,715 --> 00:14:45,537
ŠTO SI UÈINIO SADA?

138
00:14:45,572 --> 00:14:49,360
POKAZAT ÆU TI NEŠTO.

139
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:16,045
GDJE JE ONA?

140
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:18,540
KUNEM TI SE SVIM BOGOVIMA

141
00:15:18,575 --> 00:15:21,000
...UBIT ÆU TE AKO MI NE KAŽEŠ!

142
00:15:21,035 --> 00:15:23,397
KRALJU MOJ!

143
00:15:23,432 --> 00:15:26,056
OTIŠLA JE...

144
00:15:26,091 --> 00:15:28,525
...S TROJANIMA

145
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:32,560
OVAJ RIBAR JE VIDIO KAD SE UKRCALA.

146
00:15:32,595 --> 00:15:36,205
TROJANI?

147
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:39,680
MLADI PRINC PARIS,...

148
00:15:39,715 --> 00:15:42,925
PRIPREMITE MI BROD!

149
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:45,960
OKRENI BROD, VRAÆAMO SE U SPARTU.

150
00:15:45,995 --> 00:15:46,765
OKREÆI!

151
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:47,725
ÈEKAJ, ÈEKAJ!

152
00:15:47,760 --> 00:15:49,760
- BUDALO!
- SASLUŠAJ ME...!

153
00:15:49,795 --> 00:15:51,565
ZNAŠ LI ŠTO SI UÈINIO?

154
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:54,600
KOLIKO JE GODINA NAŠ OTAC RADIO
DA BI USPOSTAVIO MIR?

155
00:15:54,635 --> 00:15:57,325
VOLIM JE.

156
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:59,245
TEBI JE TO SVE IGRA?

157
00:15:59,280 --> 00:16:01,165
IDEŠ OD GRADA DO GRADA...

158
00:16:01,200 --> 00:16:03,660
ZAVODIŠ TRGOVKINJE I SVEÆENICE...

159
00:16:03,695 --> 00:16:05,347
I MISLIŠ DA ZNAŠ NEŠTO O LJUBAVI.

160
00:16:05,382 --> 00:16:06,925
ŠTO JE S LJUBAVLJU PREMA OCU?

161
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:09,960
OŠAMARIO SI GA KAD SI NJU
DOVEO NA BROD.

162
00:16:09,995 --> 00:16:12,877
ŠTO JE S LJUBAVLJU PREMA DOMOVINI?

163
00:16:12,912 --> 00:16:15,760
ŽELIŠ DA TROJA GORI ZA OVU ŽENU?!

164
00:16:17,520 --> 00:16:19,520
NEÆU TI DOPUSTITI DA ZAPOÈNEŠ RAT
ZBOG NJE.

165
00:16:19,555 --> 00:16:21,325
MOGU LI REÆI?

166
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:23,360
ISTINA JE TO ŠTO KAŽEŠ...

167
00:16:23,395 --> 00:16:24,817
...IZNEVJERIO SAM TE

168
00:16:24,852 --> 00:16:26,125
...IZNEVJERIO SAM I OCA.

169
00:16:26,160 --> 00:16:30,160
AKO ŽELIŠ DA HELENU VRATIMO
NEKA TAKO BUDE.

170
00:16:30,195 --> 00:16:32,057
ALI JA ODLAZIM S NJOM.

171
00:16:32,092 --> 00:16:33,920
SPARTANCI ÆE TE UBITI.

172
00:16:33,955 --> 00:16:35,725
BORIT ÆU SE.

173
00:16:35,760 --> 00:16:38,605
TO TI LIJEPO ZVUÈI, JUNAÈKI...

174
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:40,580
UMRIJETI U BORBI
ŠTA PRIÈAŠ, BRATE...

175
00:16:40,615 --> 00:16:42,445
- JESI LI IKADA UBIO ÈOVJEKA?
- NE

176
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,480
JESI LI VIDIO KAKO ÈOVJEK
UMIRE U BITCI?

177
00:16:44,515 --> 00:16:45,325
NE.

178
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:48,360
JA SAM UBIO ÈOVJEKA
I SLUŠAO SAM KAKO UMIRE..

179
00:16:48,395 --> 00:16:51,240
...I NEMA NIŠTA PREKRASNOG U TOME.

180
00:16:51,275 --> 00:16:52,045
NIÈEGA POETSKOGA.

181
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:54,080
KAŽEŠ DA ŽELIŠ UMRIJETI
ZA LJUBAV

182
00:16:54,115 --> 00:16:56,017
...A NEZNAŠ NIŠTA O SMRTI

183
00:16:56,052 --> 00:16:57,920
I NEZNAŠ NIŠTA O LJUBAVI.

184
00:16:57,955 --> 00:16:59,377
ISTA STVAR.

185
00:16:59,412 --> 00:17:00,685
IDEM S NJOM.

186
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:04,720
NEÆU TE TRAŽITI DA VODIŠ MOJ RAT.

187
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:08,440
UPRAVO JESI.

188
00:17:08,475 --> 00:17:11,245
PREMA TROJI!

189
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:15,280
MORNARI, NA MJESTA!

190
00:17:16,080 --> 00:17:20,080
MIKENA
GRÈKA

191
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:49,240
ŽELIM JE NATRAG.

192
00:17:49,275 --> 00:17:50,605
NARAVNO DA ŽELIŠ.

193
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:52,525
ONA JE PREKRASNA ŽENA.

194
00:17:52,560 --> 00:17:56,560
ŽELIM JE NATRAG DA BIH JE UBIO
VLASTITIM RUKAMA.

195
00:17:56,595 --> 00:17:59,437
A TROJU ÆU SRAVNITI SA ZEMLJOM.

196
00:17:59,472 --> 00:18:02,280
MISLIO SAM DA ŽELIŠ MIR S TROJOM?

197
00:18:02,315 --> 00:18:03,160
TREBAO SAM TE POSLUŠATI.

198
00:18:03,195 --> 00:18:06,077
MIR JE ZA LUDE...

199
00:18:06,112 --> 00:18:08,845
...I SLABIÆE.

200
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:10,880
IMPERIJI SE STVARAJU...

201
00:18:10,915 --> 00:18:12,685
...RATOM

202
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:14,680
CIJELI SVOJ ŽIVOT SAM UZ TEBE...

203
00:18:14,715 --> 00:18:16,640
BORIM SE PROTIV TVOJIH NEPRIJATELJA.

204
00:18:16,675 --> 00:18:20,365
POSTIGLI SMO PUNO...

205
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,860
JESAM LI SE IKAD ŽALIO, BRATE...

206
00:18:21,895 --> 00:18:23,320
JESAM LI TE IKAD IŠTA TRAŽIO?

207
00:18:23,355 --> 00:18:26,125
NIKADA

208
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:28,045
TI SI ÈASTAN ÈOVJEK.

209
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:32,080
HOÆEŠ LI RATOVAT UZ MENE, BRATE?

210
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:43,560
ODUVIJEK SAM MISLIO DA JE
BRATOVA ŽENA PRIGLUPA.

211
00:18:43,595 --> 00:18:47,440
ALI POKAZALO SE DA JE
NADASVE KORISNA.

212
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:50,200
TROJA NIKAD NIJE BILA POKORENA.

213
00:18:50,235 --> 00:18:52,045
KAŽU DA JU JE NEMOGUÆE OSVOJITI.

214
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:56,080
STARI KRALJ PRIJAM MISLI DA SI JE
POMOGAO VISOKIM ZIDINAMA

215
00:18:56,880 --> 00:19:00,880
MISLI DA ÆE MU BOG SUNCA POMOÆI.

216
00:19:00,915 --> 00:19:03,720
ALI BOGOVI ŠTITE SAMO...

217
00:19:03,755 --> 00:19:06,445
...SNAŽNE.

218
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,405
AKO TROJA PADNE

219
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:11,245
...JA VLADAM EGIPTOM.

220
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:14,125
HEKTOR ZAPOVJEDA NAJBOLJOM
VOJSKOM NA ISTOKU.

221
00:19:14,160 --> 00:19:17,160
